  "original_title": "\u0d85\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0dc0\u0ddb\u0daf\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0dc3\u0dda\u0dc0\u0dcf \u0daf\u0dd9\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0da2\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Interim medical services on strike for two days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The paramedics will go on a token strike for 48 hours from tomorrow (29) to protest against the failure of the authorities to prepare a plan to resolve fuel and transport problems.",
        "However, members of the Family Health Service are engaged in essential services in maternity wards and other hospitals, said Disnaka Dissanayake, National Organizer of the Health Entomologists Association.",
        "He added that family health workers, public health inspectors, school dentists, dental technicians, electrocardiographers, chiropractors, pharmacists and health laboratory workers representing the front would join the strike.",
        "Mr. Dissanayake said that due to the prevailing fuel crisis and the increase in transport costs, a large number of problems have arisen in the reporting of these personnel to work and field duties and the authorities have been requested on several occasions to resolve the existing problems.",
        "He further said that the authorities are not taking any action to resolve the promotion issues of these services and it has been nearly a year since the Cabinet approval was given to resolve these issues.",
        "The strike will begin at 8.00 am today and will continue for 48 hours.",
        "He further stated that if the issues are not resolved by the 5th, a continuous strike will be launched from the 5th."
      ],
